text: Lulusar-Dodipat National Park () is in the Kaghan Valley in Mansehra District of Khyber-Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan. The park was created in 2003. The scenic Dudipatsar Lake and Lulusar Lake and peaks are in the park. == Related pages == * Mansehra District Category:National parks in Pakistan Category:Mansehra District
title: Lulusar-Dudipatsar National Park
